	 Portugal Seizes More Than 6,000 Kilograms of Drugs ...

OTC  4/3/97 4:34 AM   

 LISBON (April 2) XINHUA - Portuguese police seized a total of 6,218  kilograms 
of narcotics in 1996 and arrested 3,724 people suspected of  drug trafficking, 
a police report said today. 
